Package controllers

Class PhotoController

java.lang.Object
controllers.PhotoController
public class PhotoController
extends java.lang.Object
In this page the user will be able to display any desired photo, add or remove tags, details, set a caption and move photos from one album to another
Author:
Hunter Brady, Alex Rivera
